            <h2>How It Works</h2>
            <p>The My Physician App enables the user to book appointments for local physicisan or specialist in the said radius. 
               <br> In addition it allows the user to jot down the symptomps before consulting the doctor.
                <br> Also it includes the Emergency pop up which when selected alerts the near by hospital and makes the ambulance on the door step.
              
               <br> The user can upload his/her previous medical history which helps the doctor for further case studies.
                <br> By knowing the blood group of the patient it helps for searching blood donors as well as make blood avaliable through the blood banks in case of emergency.
                </p>
               
                <h2 align="right">About The Services</h2>
                <p align="right">Patients can book appointments of the doctor available nearest to you.

                    <br>Patients can also get consultation through this website and pay the consultation charges to the doctor through the website.
    
                    <br>Doctors can treat the patients by making appointments available to them and also provide the consultattion through the website.
    
                    <br>Patients can also receive emergency services at their doorstep.</p>
